title: Seetharamam
subTitle: Afreen, a Pakistani woman, heads to India in order to deliver a love letter written in 1965 to fulfill her grandfather's dying wish. However, the journey alters her life forever.

title: Yajamana
subTitle: Devi Shetty, a cruel gangster, is out to plunder a village's oil resources and ruin its inhabitants' livelihood. However, the son-in-law of the village head, Krishna, stands in his way.

title: Doshi
subTitle: A man's life falls into danger when he accidentally takes a photo of a murder committed by a gangster. The latter then kidnaps his lover in exchange for the evidence.
